    {
      "instruction": "<p>Season the <strong>cubed paneer </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, then drizzle with a little <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and press them into the <strong>ground coconut mix </strong>firmly to evenly coat all over – this is your <strong>coated paneer</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
