    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated paneer</strong> and cook for 5-6 min until golden, turning occasionally for even colouring</p>",
