    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the paneer is cooking, combine your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong>, <strong>rice vinegar </strong>and <strong>remaining curry powder </strong>in a large bowl</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar </strong>and mix it all together – this is your <strong>curried dressing</strong></p>",
