    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add your <strong>mooli slaw mix </strong>and <strong>chopped coriander </strong>to the <strong>curried dressing </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>curried slaw</strong></p>",
